headline: Western Digital Advances Ecosystem Collaboration, Innovation for AI Acceleration, Disaggregated Storage and SDS at Computex 2025
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif. & TAIPEI, Taiwan, May 19, 2025--Computex 2025 – Western Digital (Nasdaq: WDC) is redefining what’s possible in storage infrastructure for AI/ML, disaggregated storage and software-defined storage (SDS) for CSPs, enterprises and STaaS providers. From massive-capacity, reliable JBODs (Just a Bunch of Disks) to ultra-fast EBOF (Ethernet Bunch of Flash) NVMe-oF™ disaggregated storage solutions for AI, the company’s Platforms Business delivers world-class HDD- and SSD-based solutions
